[holderhost LTD](https://holderhost.com) was formed in July 2012. If it is quality services you're seeking, then holderhost delivers. We are always looking to improve to ensure we offer fast, reliable and affordable hosting for our clients.
&lt;br&gt;
Our new XEN offering is very limited and will not be marketed on our website because of this. 


&lt;h2&gt;Plan:&lt;/h2&gt;

**Unmanaged XEN PV**

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2GB RAM&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;70 GB Disk&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1 H/T Dedicated Core&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1TB Bandwidth @ 1Gbps&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2 IPs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
Price: $7/mo | [ORDER](https://holderhost.com/clients/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=57)

~You are fully welcome to order multiple and have them combined. Just open a ticket.

&lt;h2&gt;Node Specs:&lt;/h2&gt;
48GB Ram&lt;br&gt;
Dual Intel Xeon X5650 24 Core Dedicated Processors&lt;br&gt;
4xTB HDD RAID10&lt;br&gt;
1Gbps Port&lt;br&gt;
Location: Wilkes-Barre, PA&lt;br&gt;
DDOS Protected&lt;br&gt;

**Available Addons**&lt;br&gt;
Additional IPs: $1.5/mo each.&lt;br&gt;
DirectAdmin: $6/mo.
&lt;br&gt;

&lt;h2&gt;What's the Catch?&lt;/h2&gt;
Well, the plan’s limited to 1 Node. There will be 23 VPSes deployed on this node MAX. That's it unfortunately. :( 

We will also not be entertaining rDNS requests for this plan.

**Important Links**:

[**AUP**](http://holderhost.com/clients/knowledgebase.php?action=displayarticle&amp;id=13) |  [**TOS** ](http://holderhost.com/clients/knowledgebase.php?action=displayarticle&amp;id=12) | 
[**Privacy Policy** ](http://holderhost.com/clients/knowledgebase.php?action=displayarticle&amp;id=10)

Our TOS/ AUP was designed for our OpenVZ offerings. You are 100% able to fully use the H/T core assigned to you. The following are **ALLOWED** on this plan: Gameservers, IRC.

Quick AUP: Public Proxies, Public VPNs, Public Torrenting, TOR are not allowed. Nothing Illegal in the US (including Spamming). 

We try to be as transparent as possible. Any questions- please feel free to ask!
